The paper discusses caching in information-centric networking (ICN), which is a subfield of computer networking. Therefore, cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses game theory and optimization, which are common in the subfields of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), and Information Theory (cs.IT).
